{"tid":629721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女愛伊斯蘭國「俠義風骨」甘願做性奴","createTime":"2018-04-15T03:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T04:27:40.000Z","uid":25345,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70336823ced66b5a1a64dc84629ec5124d898717","tid":629721,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ve2HJT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fve2HJT.jpg&h=a6e0d2b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國巴黎遭受伊斯蘭國恐怖份子襲擊，造成129人死亡，正當全球民眾均報以哀悼，並譴責是次恐襲，有港女竟然持相反意見，並表明「愛上伊斯蘭國的俠義風骨，就像金庸先生筆下小說的現實版」<br />\n<br />\n該港女直言「不同情法國」，更批評大家將facebook頭像轉為法國國旗的紅白藍3色，行為「膚淺」。她續指「沒有人出生就夢想做恐怖份子」，不過正正因為現實世界「黑暗得太黑暗」，因此才會愛上「伊斯蘭國的俠義風骨」，更形容恐襲等同「金庸先生筆下小說的現實版」。"},{"pid":"fff4f9c29035f9bb7da38e82e752fd14c1deed95","tid":629721,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"又bin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2355b48a04c8286c0b6d1602d84ab977d49564","tid":629721,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"而家已經係2018年"},{"pid":"1f4a87a857731a4672e5aa8d45119b33ef213255","tid":629721,"uid":57835,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"唔好亂作標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9485644b90a7243939587955baea5c60c51fa598","tid":629721,"uid":17270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"f0c2c3f16d79130ed3418a188c8330f564ebe3a9","tid":629721,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:26:05.000Z","msg":"又loop"},{"pid":"ae0449c05623e728876d953cca2185379ac3a74e","tid":629721,"uid":150194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:29:00.000Z","ms